name: Senka Champion - Zhang De
desc:
Gains 300 ATK for each monster your opponent controls during your turn only. You can only use each of the following effects of "Senka Champion - Zhang De" once per turn.
● If you control 2 or more "Senka" monsters: You can Special Summon this card from your hand.
● If your opponent controls more monsters than you do: You can activate this effect; this card can make up to 2 attacks on monsters during each Battle Phase this turn.
